	Scarlett locks    
	 London, July 18 (PTI): Actress Scarlett Johansson has ditched her golden locks to turn into a raunchy redhead for her coming film Iron Man 2.      
	The 23-year-old star, who is seen in a skin-tight cat suit in a still from the film, has dyed her blonde hair for the more fiery look to become The Black Widow in the comic book sequel, The Sun reports. The actress is also working out for the role as the flexible Russian super spy.    
	Kylie slap    
	 New York (PTI): Trouble seems to have erupted in the love paradise of Kylie Minogue and her Spanish toyboy Andres Velencoso after the pint-sized pop star was seen slapping the model. One shocked onlooker said: At some point, Kylie and Andres got separated. When Kylie found him, she slapped him in the face with a fan.    
	Mel mate    
	 Los Angeles (PTI): After Mel Gibson, it is his estranged wife Robyns turn to move on from her failed marriage. Robyn has reportedly found love with a Californian man and has even introduced him to her children.                                                                                                                                                                        
